{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And yet, you know, when people talk about the resistance, I associate resistance with our existence, with our attempt to remain human, with our attempt to preserve our humanity, with holding on to our values.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To me, that was a resistance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because when we went to-- we, we had hidden schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I also-- before I, I, I, I will share with you about the hidden schools, I would like to also list some of the other things that occurred that come to mind.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were rations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were armbands.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had to wear a, a, a, a, a band with-- on, on, on our arm always, always.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as children, we must not forget-- with the Star of David.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I think there was pride in the Star of David, gave us the identification.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But not the way-- not-- it, it, it was humiliating to use it as, as, as, as, as, as a print like you put on cattle, like a number on a-- on cattle.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] The, the, the, the first-- the Jewish community really organized itself very quickly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There were committees formed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were committees formed in every building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was the Jewish committee, like a Jewish Community Center.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was like a Jewish government, which, in some ways, the Germans supported because it was their way of, of communicating with the-- with the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Very often, the Germans would pass on mandates to the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they had to carry it out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I don't recall the name of the president of the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I, I hope that I recall during the interview, because he was a very decent person.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
